attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: This well-designed condominium offers nearly 1700 square feet of living space with 2+ bedrooms and two full bathrooms and 2 private outdoor spaces. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, kitchen, and private balcony, providing ample space for entertaining. The primary bedroom features a spacious layout with a private en-suite bathroom, while the additional two bedrooms share a convenient full bathroom. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, and custom cabinetry, making meal preparation a delight. The community amenities include a common roof deck as well as a PRIVATE ROOF DECK section exclusively for this unit and one deeded Garage Parking space.  This property is ideal for those seeking a comfortable and low-maintenance lifestyle in a desirable location.

exclusions: Front Door Lamp And Book Shelf To Right Of Kitchen
